==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outpace
<hw>Out*pace"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Outpass</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To outgo; to move faster than;
to leave behind.</def> <rj><au>Lamb.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To exceed in development or performance; to
outdo.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outparamour</ent>⟦br⟧
